rows.label: bf07280100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp]

rows.label: bf07280100_0020
rows.name: My lady...

rows.label: bf07280100_0030
rows.name:
I told you I'm fine!
Byakko, why don't you worry about yourself instead?

rows.label: bf07280100_0040
rows.name: But...

rows.label: bf07280100_0042
rows.name:
You gotta admire Turtle-chan over there.
He just put it right out there.

rows.label: bf07280100_0044
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hmm?

rows.label: bf07280100_0046
rows.name: And in contrast...

rows.label: bf07280100_0048
rows.name: Byakko...

rows.label: bf07280100_0050
rows.name:
I'm gonna put myself to the test.
Right here. I've decided.

rows.label: bf07280100_0055
rows.name: My lady...

rows.label: bf07280100_0060
rows.name: I understand...

rows.label: bf07280100_0070
rows.name:
The mist is thick.
It's like we're inside the Cloud Sea.

rows.label: bf07280100_0080
rows.name:
It seems to be produced by the fossilized Divine 
Beast's body reacting with the atmosphere.

rows.label: bf07280100_0090
rows.name: That's probably why it's hard to breathe.

rows.label: bf07280100_0100
rows.name: [ML:undisp]

rows.label: bf07280100_0110
rows.name: Nia?

rows.label: bf07280100_0120
rows.name: ...What is it?

rows.label: bf07280100_0130
rows.name: Are you in pain?

rows.label: bf07280100_0140
rows.name: I can hardly breathe, you know.

rows.label: bf07280100_0150
rows.name: Well... I might be a little dizzy, but that's all.

rows.label: bf07280100_0160
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: bf07280100_0170
rows.name:
At times like that, it's best not to think 
about anything and just empty your mind.

rows.label: bf07280100_0180
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf07280100_0190
rows.name: It's a basic salvager technique.

rows.label: bf07280100_0200
rows.name:
When you dive deep, your brain 
feels like it's being squeezed.

rows.label: bf07280100_0210
rows.name:
If you try not to think too much, 
the pressure won't bother you as much.

rows.label: bf07280100_0220
rows.name: It makes things a bit easier.

rows.label: bf07280100_0230
rows.name: Empty my head, huh...

rows.label: bf07280100_0240
rows.name:
So you're saying 
I should be an idiot like you, Rex?

rows.label: bf07280100_0250
rows.name: That's impossible for me.

rows.label: bf07280100_0260
rows.name: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?

rows.label: bf07280100_0270
rows.name:
Everyone!
Come over here!

rows.label: bf07280100_0280
rows.name: Looks like we can go down through this hole, mo.

rows.label: bf07280100_0290
rows.name:
It looks like someone intentionally
created this opening.

rows.label: bf07280100_0300
rows.name: Grave robbers or something?

rows.label: bf07280100_0310
rows.name:
There's nothing worth stealing here.
Unless...

rows.label: bf07280100_0320
rows.name: Something related to Adel and Homura.

rows.label: bf07280100_0330
rows.name: It's just speculation, but...

rows.label: bf07280100_0340
rows.name: Perhaps Shin and his group have been here before.

rows.label: bf07280100_0350
rows.name:
Then...they found out about the sunken ship,
and went to Avaritia.

rows.label: bf07280100_0360
rows.name: It's still just speculation, mind you.

rows.label: bf07280100_0370
rows.name: If that's the case, there might be nothing ahead.

rows.label: bf07280100_0380
rows.name:
If that were true, 
they should already have the third sword.

rows.label: bf07280100_0390
rows.name: But they didn't have it...

rows.label: bf07280100_0400
rows.name:
I doubt that Adel would have
made it so easy for it to be taken.

rows.label: bf07280100_0410
rows.name:
Let's keep going.
It'll be fine, I'm sure.
